<p>Assuming $n = 2^q$ for some $q \geq 1$, we have</p>

\[\begin{align*}
        T(n) &amp;= k\left[ T\left(\frac{n}{2^1} \right) \right] + f(n) \\\\
        &amp;= k\left[k\left[ T\left(\frac{n}{2^2} \right) \right] + f(n) \right] + f(n) \\\\
        &amp;= k\left[k\left[k\left[ T\left(\frac{n}{2^3} \right) \right] + f(n) \right] + f(n)  \right] + f(n) \\
        &amp;\vdots \\
        &amp;= k^q\left[ T\left(\frac{n}{2^q} \right) \right] + k^{q - 1}f(n) + k^{q - 2}f(n) + \cdots + kf(n) + f(n) \\\\
        &amp;= 
    \end{align*}\]

\[\qed\]
